1
00:00:10,860 --> 00:00:12,780
♪The wind blows, but I don't see you♪

2
00:00:12,820 --> 00:00:14,740
♪I added a few more strokes♪

3
00:00:14,740 --> 00:00:17,380
♪To the ending♪

4
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:21,580
♪With the flowers falling
and the time passing♪

5
00:00:21,860 --> 00:00:24,140
♪Leaving only memories behind♪

6
00:00:24,300 --> 00:00:28,220
♪The wind blows from a long distance♪

7
00:00:28,340 --> 00:00:31,020
♪Yet, you didn't show up♪

8
00:00:31,140 --> 00:00:33,140
♪This love is full of regrets♪

9
00:00:33,300 --> 00:00:37,420
♪You are but a dream
in this fleeting life♪

10
00:00:40,260 --> 00:00:41,260
[Part For Ever]

11
00:00:41,260 --> 00:00:42,000
[Adapted from the novel by Jing Mo,]

12
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:42,900
[My Lord,
Madam Doesn't Want to See You Again]

13
00:00:42,900 --> 00:00:44,780
[Episode 16]

14
00:00:44,780 --> 00:00:51,200
[City Lord's Mansion]

15
00:00:51,200 --> 00:00:52,200
Sinner Niyue,

16
00:00:52,350 --> 00:00:53,390
with a heart as venomous as a snake,

17
00:00:53,670 --> 00:00:54,920
repeatedly framed Su Wan'er,

18
00:00:55,390 --> 00:00:56,710
concealed the virginity mark,

19
00:00:56,710 --> 00:00:57,640
and deceived His Lordship.

20
00:00:58,070 --> 00:00:59,840
The lighter punishment
is banishment from Canglong City,

21
00:01:00,350 --> 00:01:01,350
and the heavier punishment is execution.

22
00:01:02,280 --> 00:01:03,320
Please make a decision, My Lord.

23
00:01:05,150 --> 00:01:06,000
Miss Wan'er,

24
00:01:06,230 --> 00:01:07,040
please save me.

25
00:01:07,430 --> 00:01:08,400
I know I deserve to die,

26
00:01:08,790 --> 00:01:09,590
and I am not worthy of pity.

27
00:01:10,150 --> 00:01:11,480
I shouldn't have taken your place

28
00:01:11,480 --> 00:01:12,760
and stayed by Ling's side,

29
00:01:13,150 --> 00:01:13,840
and I shouldn't have...

30
00:01:14,230 --> 00:01:16,000
I shouldn't have pretended
to have slept with him.

31
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:18,280
It's all my fault.

32
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:21,430
That day,

33
00:01:21,430 --> 00:01:23,400
you left behind
the rabbit pendant in despair.

34
00:01:23,590 --> 00:01:24,950
I'm returning it
to its rightful owner now.

35
00:01:31,040 --> 00:01:32,510
I will leave Canglong City immediately.

36
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:34,310
Please spare my life.

37
00:01:53,740 --> 00:01:59,700
♪People sit silently by candlelight
as night begins♪

38
00:01:59,820 --> 00:02:05,620
♪A play of sorrows and joys,
your role, my outline♪

39
00:02:05,660 --> 00:02:10,860
♪Though the dream is over,
the feelings are hard to let go♪

40
00:02:10,940 --> 00:02:12,540
♪Everyone is filled
with sorrow and pity♪

41
00:02:12,620 --> 00:02:16,420
♪Alas, the mortal world
has too many spectators♪

42
00:02:17,660 --> 00:02:23,540
♪You turn back to ascend
the stage wearing a green robe♪

43
00:02:23,740 --> 00:02:29,300
♪A song asking about heart matters,
but who will answer?♪

44
00:02:29,780 --> 00:02:35,100
♪An old dream with infatuation
and resentment and complications♪

45
00:02:35,180 --> 00:02:36,540
♪You sing for me♪

46
00:02:36,620 --> 00:02:40,540
♪In the play,
telling of separations and reunions♪

47
00:02:42,470 --> 00:02:43,310
Wan'er,

48
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:45,240
do you still remember

49
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:46,960
the fireflies we saw

50
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:48,120
in the cave back then?

51
00:02:50,310 --> 00:02:51,960
That day also felt

52
00:02:52,430 --> 00:02:53,680
as surreal as today.

53
00:02:57,710 --> 00:02:58,400
On that day,

54
00:02:59,430 --> 00:03:00,960
we both talked about the past,

55
00:03:01,710 --> 00:03:02,520
but we didn't realize

56
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:05,840
that we were
the most important people to each other.

57
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:09,360
Fortunately,

58
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:12,840
after all these years,

59
00:03:14,030 --> 00:03:15,630
fate has brought us
back together again.

60
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:30,310
Actually, I...

61
00:03:36,870 --> 00:03:38,150
You go first.

62
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:43,870
Wan'er,

63
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:45,840
I want

64
00:03:46,590 --> 00:03:47,800
to apologize to you.

65
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:51,150
I've done

66
00:03:52,750 --> 00:03:54,680
a lot of things to hurt you

67
00:03:55,750 --> 00:03:58,470
and said many things I didn't mean.

68
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:00,630
I misjudged people,

69
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:03,710
causing us to miss out
on so many years.

70
00:04:05,030 --> 00:04:05,840
Wan'er,

71
00:04:08,190 --> 00:04:09,470
I've made you sad and upset.

72
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:11,470
I'm sorry.

73
00:04:13,750 --> 00:04:15,030
I didn't believe you,

74
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:17,560
and ended up causing
a lot of misunderstandings.

75
00:04:18,950 --> 00:04:19,750
I'm also at fault.

76
00:04:19,750 --> 00:04:20,480
Stop.

77
00:04:20,870 --> 00:04:22,680
I've already apologized verbally.

78
00:04:23,310 --> 00:04:24,160
Now,

79
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,920
you can only express your apology
through actions.

80
00:04:27,870 --> 00:04:29,360
Like what actions?

81
00:04:31,270 --> 00:04:32,070
Like...

82
00:04:35,700 --> 00:04:40,900
♪I'm afraid the characters
in the play aren't us♪

83
00:05:33,630 --> 00:05:35,360
Do you like my actions?

84
00:05:36,940 --> 00:05:39,820
♪The lush and fragrant grass
made longing hard to endure♪

85
00:05:39,980 --> 00:05:43,380
♪Can I entrust my heart to you?♪

86
00:05:43,460 --> 00:05:46,340
♪This love is hard to fade away
as it twists and turns endlessly♪

87
00:05:46,420 --> 00:05:49,700
♪On the path of emotions♪

88
00:05:49,820 --> 00:05:53,500
♪Reflected in a mirror
by moonlight through a window♪

89
00:05:53,660 --> 00:05:56,380
♪How much is your affection?♪

90
00:05:56,620 --> 00:06:02,740
♪When the time to love is not right,
worldly matters make it hard to endure♪

91
00:06:02,820 --> 00:06:05,460
♪Amid all worldly matters,
I only devote to one person♪

92
00:06:05,540 --> 00:06:10,300
♪Love is silent, but it leaves traces
as deep as the sea♪

93
00:06:10,420 --> 00:06:16,100
♪I accompany you
for a part of the journey♪

94
00:06:16,220 --> 00:06:18,580
♪Our longing for each other
guides us through countless lives♪

95
00:06:18,700 --> 00:06:23,700
♪The flowers of the entire city
blossom for a person♪

96
00:06:23,820 --> 00:06:29,100
♪Let's spend
the rest of our lives together♪

97
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:41,600
Wan'er,

98
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:43,000
take care of yourself.

99
00:06:43,510 --> 00:06:44,950
I apologize to you on his behalf.

100
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:50,160
I only want him to treat you well.

101
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:53,270
As for the rest, it's all in the past.

102
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,160
Your ten minutes

103
00:06:57,920 --> 00:06:58,560
are up.

104
00:06:59,240 --> 00:06:59,830
Ling Xiao,

105
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:01,680
you better treat Wan'er well.

106
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:03,560
If she suffers even a little,

107
00:07:04,270 --> 00:07:05,630
I won't let you off.

108
00:07:21,830 --> 00:07:22,800
From now on,

109
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:25,240
your breath should only have me in it.

110
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:27,040
When you open your eyes,

111
00:07:27,430 --> 00:07:28,360
you should only see me.

112
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:31,160
You too.

113
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:32,800
Naturally.

114
00:07:34,160 --> 00:07:34,720
Now that

115
00:07:35,190 --> 00:07:37,190
Jing Tian has returned to Baiyu City
to inherit the position of City Lord,

116
00:07:37,750 --> 00:07:38,720
and Niyue has been sent away by me.

117
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:39,720
There will be

118
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:42,830
no one standing between us anymore.

119
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:48,680
I have prepared a surprise for you.

120
00:07:53,630 --> 00:07:55,000
Where are you taking me?

121
00:07:57,390 --> 00:07:58,360
It smells so nice.

122
00:07:58,950 --> 00:07:59,870
It's the scent of flowers.

123
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:09,950
Do you like it?

124
00:08:11,830 --> 00:08:13,000
Such a beautiful flower garden.

125
00:08:14,240 --> 00:08:15,040
It may be beautiful here,

126
00:08:18,190 --> 00:08:19,750
but it's not half
as beautiful as you.

127
00:08:24,430 --> 00:08:25,390
You once said that you wanted

128
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:26,920
to play the Guqin, wield the sword

129
00:08:27,190 --> 00:08:28,360
and admire the flowers

130
00:08:28,510 --> 00:08:30,270
with the young man in your heart.

131
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:31,720
Now,

132
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:33,550
shall we realize your wishes together?

133
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:48,080
With the heaven and earth,

134
00:08:48,510 --> 00:08:49,510
the sun and moon as witnesses,

135
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:52,200
I, Ling Xiao, swear

136
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:54,030
to love only Su Wan'er

137
00:08:54,630 --> 00:08:55,840
in this lifetime.

138
00:08:56,790 --> 00:08:57,910
My heart belongs solely

139
00:08:58,750 --> 00:09:00,080
to Wan'er for eternity.

140
00:09:01,390 --> 00:09:03,360
Even if the time
we have together is fleeting like flowers,

141
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:05,390
my love for Wan'er

142
00:09:06,550 --> 00:09:07,600
will endure endlessly.

143
00:09:08,750 --> 00:09:11,200
And I you.

144
00:09:11,220 --> 00:09:17,180
♪When the time to love is not right,
worldly matters make it hard to endure♪

145
00:09:17,300 --> 00:09:19,940
♪Amid all worldly matters,
I only devote to one person♪

146
00:09:20,020 --> 00:09:24,700
♪Love is silent, but it leaves traces
as deep as the sea♪

147
00:09:24,980 --> 00:09:30,540
♪I accompany you
for a part of the journey♪

148
00:09:30,660 --> 00:09:33,060
♪Our longing for each other
guides us through countless lives♪

149
00:09:33,220 --> 00:09:37,900
♪The flowers of the entire city
blossom for a person♪

150
00:09:38,380 --> 00:09:43,620
♪Let's spend
the rest of our lives together♪

151
00:09:58,300 --> 00:10:01,220
♪My dream is rising
in my heart like a spiral♪

152
00:10:01,340 --> 00:10:04,500
♪The fate of our meeting
has been decided♪

153
00:10:06,510 --> 00:10:07,510
Once,

154
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:10,150
I had an unforgettable encounter

155
00:10:10,480 --> 00:10:12,390
with a young man.

156
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:15,510
For a moment,

157
00:10:15,870 --> 00:10:19,270
I imagined brewing tea, making wine,

158
00:10:19,750 --> 00:10:21,120
playing the Guqin, wielding the sword,

159
00:10:21,870 --> 00:10:23,720
and admiring the flowers
together with him.

160
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:27,150
Unexpectedly,

161
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:29,840
everything I longed for back then,

162
00:10:30,550 --> 00:10:32,870
he has now helped me realize one by one.

163
00:10:38,150 --> 00:10:39,440
The man before me is

164
00:10:40,270 --> 00:10:42,120
the joy of my youth

165
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:44,270
and will be

166
00:10:44,670 --> 00:10:46,480
my lifelong partner.

167
00:10:50,700 --> 00:10:53,140
♪Amid all worldly matters,
I only devote to one person♪

168
00:10:53,380 --> 00:10:58,060
♪Love is silent, but it leaves traces
as deep as the sea♪

169
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:02,910
How come there are
so many peach blossoms here,

170
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:04,390
and even tall lotus leaves?

171
00:11:05,080 --> 00:11:06,600
I had someone to irrigate them
with hot spring water.

172
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:08,320
So that this garden

173
00:11:08,870 --> 00:11:09,870
would bloom for you.

174
00:11:11,660 --> 00:11:17,260
♪Let's spend
the rest of our lives together♪

175
00:11:43,060 --> 00:11:44,820
♪White dew penetrates the sandalwood♪

176
00:11:44,940 --> 00:11:46,500
♪Heading to the garden alone♪

177
00:11:46,540 --> 00:11:49,660
♪The Guqin is playing among the trees♪

178
00:11:49,780 --> 00:11:51,580
♪And the cicadas chirp
deep in the bamboo courtyard♪

179
00:11:51,660 --> 00:11:54,540
♪A person inside a door♪

180
00:11:56,340 --> 00:11:59,820
♪As we see the falling leaves♪

181
00:11:59,900 --> 00:12:03,180
♪Threads of memories surround us♪

182
00:12:03,180 --> 00:12:08,460
♪They become a cocoon to wrap around us♪

183
00:12:09,820 --> 00:12:13,260
♪Putting on makeup as the bright moon
scattered its light on the sky♪

184
00:12:13,340 --> 00:12:16,300
♪Like white frost♪

185
00:12:16,820 --> 00:12:21,300
♪I look afar as my thoughts fly past
like white snow♪

186
00:12:22,460 --> 00:12:25,900
♪Looking through the window, the letter
I wrote is short, yet my love persists♪

187
00:12:26,460 --> 00:12:29,380
♪Thinking of you
dancing in colorful clothes♪

188
00:12:29,940 --> 00:12:34,580
♪Sending it to the distant place
where I long to go but cannot reach♪

189
00:12:35,940 --> 00:12:38,340
♪I was a youth when I started writing♪

190
00:12:38,420 --> 00:12:42,580
♪Falling in love,
there are too many deep memories♪

191
00:12:43,220 --> 00:12:45,300
♪When I stopped writing,
I was the only one aware♪

192
00:12:45,340 --> 00:12:49,420
♪Of my purpose in this life,
and fate is not true♪
